releaseNotes:
#  (2023-07-19)


### Bug Fixes

* Adjust path conversion for WSL (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/52ba907809c1b23f14d1112adc232a31f7e59754)
* Adjust response file for aot-instances (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/e11878a5a81bb3acbe29edf792f2408ad7fd7f48)
* Default image should be relative to Uno Platform domain (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/2142b63749aea586f7307f3b8a2119f8cedf84e0)
* Don't depend on Microsoft.AspNetCore.App (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/f0ff7a9867e0117ed5d71a14c87287bee085b445)
* **extensionless:** Adjust for filename-only renaming (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/1492d9b87e839a6dceeacd5a071a17f2a4be404a)
* **obj:** Remove invalid obj files in nuspec (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/017b79ea0685e658fb725c7ca303f51ee8f7066b)
* Remove dependency on csc (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/c26ad0e8391460ccccf6786c7c93b3c01f46a551)
* **tuner:** Don't copy the tuner binaries in the runtime tools folder (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/1b157b04abede7fd7c7a41afc8a53c0240868f32)
* Url relative to uno platform domain (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/d0d5e9db4cf4da28bbb12095775351e19569b5da)
* **windows:** Adjust tuner invocations to use a response file (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/c2ddc2c35a8e41a0030bd7b239e6a30f991ba760)
* **wsl:** Adjust support for missing net7 linker binaries (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/acb218ae5d02b279b878ea2ad1cf4619d22f2648)


### Features

* Add support for WebAssemblyHttpRequestMessageExtensions (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/b0bc6fcea621ecdbb175718627aa1fec72189b86)
* **obfuscation:** Adds support for extension-less assembly URIs (https://github.com/unoplatform/Uno.Wasm.Bootstrap/commit/0e790900c7bb1860201c42d7fb1073126cdc6675)
